article_id:785,category_name:News,title_name:Build Dojos in the Castle Grounds to Increase Your Might!,image_path:,message:<div>To commemorate the first anniversary, we&#39;re giving all players a gift of items that will be useful for constructing and leveling up dojos.</div><div><br></div><div>Constructing the various weapon dojos in your castle grounds increases the HP and strength of adventurers with the corresponding weapon type.</div><div><br></div><div>To get the various weapon dojos, select the Shop from the Home page, then tap Treasure Trade. You can trade for them under The Imperial Onslaught.</div><div>Note: You must complete Chapter 6 of the main campaign. There are exchange limits.</div><div><br></div><div>Construct and level up dojos to bolster your teams!</div><div><br></div><div>â– Gift</div><div>Dyrenell Aureus x100</div><div>Dyrenell Argenteus x200</div><div>Dyrenell Aes x300</div><div>Rupies x1,000,000</div><div><br></div><div>These gifts will be sent to all players who started the game by <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569996000"></span> and can be claimed for up to 7 days after reception. If the gift isn&rsquo;t retrieved within seven days, it will be lost.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1569996000,update_time1570010939